ing: 1 avocado - peeled, pitted, and coarsely chopped
1/4 teaspoon salt, or more to taste
1/4 teaspoon ground black pepper, or more to taste
des: "A perfect no-cook soup for a hot summer day! A great way to use and serve bountiful garden zucchini! The garbanzo beans add substance, texture, and protein too. Garnish with sour cream and freshly ground black pepper, if desired."
ins: Combine zucchini, onion, avocado, garbanzo beans, apple cider vinegar, jalapeno pepper, lemon juice, garlic, salt, and pepper together in a bowl; chill in refrigerator for at least 1 hour.
